                    "text": "If a creature critically succeeds on a check to <a aonid=\"40\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Trip</a> the giant crab, the crab is flipped over onto its back in addition to the usual effects. A giant crab that is flipped onto its back has a particularly hard time defending itself; instead of taking the normal \u20132 circumstance penalty to AC for being <a aonid=\"16\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">flat-footed</a>, it takes a \u20134 circumstance penalty to AC."
